---
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
	<Header />

	<!--=====|| Main Section Start ||=====-->
	<main class="page">
		<section class="privacy-policy">
			<div class="container">
				<h1 class="section-title__xl">Privacy Policy </h1>

				<p class="fs-22 fw-600 mt-md-30 mt-10"
					><span class="text-primary">Last Updated:</span>
					<span class="fw-500">June 30, 2025</span>
				</p>
				<p class="fs-22 fw-600 mt-md-30 mt-10"
					><span class="text-primary">Website:</span>
					<a class="text-dark fw-500" href="https://wellnessplusrx.com"
						>https://wellnessplusrx.com</a
					></p
				>
				<div class="mt-md-30 mt-0">
					<p class="fs-22">
						Welcome to <strong>Wellness Plus by ThriveWell RX</strong> ("Wellness
						Plus", "we", "our", or "us"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect,
						use, and protect your personal information when you interact with our
						website, services, and communication channels, including text messaging.
						By using our services, you agree to the terms outlined in this policy.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="privacy-policy__items mt-md-50 mt-20">
					<p class="fs-md-28 fs-sm-20 fs-16 fw-600 mb-0">1. Who We Are </p>
					<p
						>Wellness Plus is a product of <strong>ThriveWell RX</strong>, a
						health and wellness company providing medically supervised weight
						loss, peptide therapy, and men’s and women’s health services across
						the United States.</p
					>
				</div>
				<!--Items ENd -->

				<div class="privacy-policy__items mt-md-50 mt-20">
					<p class="fs-md-28 fs-sm-20 fs-16 fw-600 mb-0"
						>2. Information We Collect
					</p>
					<p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
					<ul class="list__items--text">
						<li
							><span class="fw-600">Personal Identification Information</span> (Name,
							email, phone number, address)
						</li>
						<li
							><span class="fw-600">Medical & Health Information</span> (via secure
							intake forms)</li
						>
						<li
							><span class="fw-600">Payment Details </span>(processed through
							secure third-party platforms)</li
						>
						<li
							><span class="fw-600">Device & Usage Data</span> (browser type, device,
							IP address)</li
						>
						<li
							><span class="fw-600">Communication Preferences</span> (including SMS
							consent, support queries, and interactions)</li
						>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<!--Items ENd -->

				<div class="privacy-policy__items mt-md-50 mt-20">
					<p class="fs-md-28 fs-sm-20 fs-16 fw-600 mb-0"
						>3. How We Use Your Information
					</p>
					<p>We use the collected information to: </p>
					<ul class="list__items--text">
						<li>Provide and manage services</li>
						<li>Facilitate doctor consultations and prescriptions</li>
						<li>Ship medications through licensed pharmacies</li>
						<li>Communicate with you via email, SMS, or phone</li>
						<li>Respond to customer service inquiries</li>
						<li>Comply with legal and regulatory obligations</li>
					</ul>
					<!--Items ENd -->

					<div class="privacy-policy__items mt-md-50 mt-20">
						<p class="fs-md-28 fs-sm-20 fs-16 fw-600 mb-0"
							>4. SMS and Text Message Communication
						</p>
						<p
							>If you provide your phone number, you may receive SMS messages
							from Wellness Plus for:
						</p>
						<ul class="list__items--text">
							<li>Intake form reminders</li>
							<li>Order and shipping updates</li>
							<li>Refill alerts</li>
							<li>Customer support follow-ups</li>
						</ul>
						<p class="fw-600 mt-md-30 mt-10">Text message compliance note:</p>
						<ul class="list__items--text">
							<li>Message frequency may vary.</li>
							<li>Message and data rates may apply.</li>
							<li>You may opt out at any time by replying STOP.</li>
							<li
								>Your SMS opt-in consent data will be kept private and not
								shared with any third parties.</li
							>
						</ul>
						<p class="fw-600 mt-md-30 mt-10"
							>SMS Clause (per carrier compliance):
						</p>
						<p
							>“All the above categories exclude text messaging originator
							opt-in data and consent; this information will not be shared with
							any third parties.”</p
						>
					</div>
					<!--Items ENd -->

					<div class="privacy-policy__items mt-md-50 mt-20">
						<p class="fs-md-28 fs-sm-20 fs-16 fw-600 mb-0"
							>5. Sharing of Information</p
						>
						<p>We may share your information with: </p>
						<ul class="list__items--text">
							<li>Licensed healthcare providers for review and prescription</li>
							<li>Licensed U.S. pharmacies for fulfillment</li>
							<li>Third-party services for secure payments and logistics </li>
							<li
								>We do not sell or rent your personal data to third parties.</li
							>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<!--Items ENd -->

					<div class="privacy-policy__items mt-md-50 mt-20">
						<p class="fs-md-28 fs-sm-20 fs-16 fw-600 mb-0"
							>6. Data Protection & Security
						</p>
						<p
							>We implement technical and organizational measures to protect
							your data, including:
						</p>
						<ul class="list__items--text">
							<li>HIPAA-compliant systems</li>
							<li>Secure data storage and encrypted transmission</li>
							<li>Role-based access to sensitive data</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<!--Items ENd -->

					<div class="privacy-policy__items mt-md-50 mt-20">
						<p class="fs-md-28 fs-sm-20 fs-16 fw-600 mb-0">7. Your Rights </p>
						<p>You have the right to: </p>
						<ul class="list__items--text">
							<li>Access or correct your information</li>
							<li>Request data deletion</li>
							<li>Withdraw consent (including SMS opt-out)</li>
							<li>Contact our support team regarding privacy concerns</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<!--Items ENd -->

					<div class="privacy-policy__items mt-md-50 mt-20">
						<p class="fs-md-28 fs-sm-20 fs-16 fw-600 mb-0">8. Contact Us </p>
						<p
							>If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy,
							please contact:</p
						>
						<p class="fw-700 mb-0">Support Team </p>
						<p class="mb-0">Wellness Plus by ThriveWell RX </p>
						<a class="fs-18 text-dark" href="mailto: support@wellnessplusrx.com
"
							>support@wellnessplusrx.com
						</a>
						<p
							><a
								class="fs-18 text-dark"
								href="mailto: support@wellnessplusrx.com
							"
								>https://wellnessplusrx.com
							</a></p
						>
					</div>
					<!--Items ENd -->
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		<!--=====|| Main Section End ||=====-->

		<Footer />
	</main>
</Layout>
